## Why Use Playbooks Instead of Ad-Hoc Commands?

### Answer

Playbooks provide reusable, version-controlled, structured automation that can execute multiple tasks in sequence. They are easier to maintain, scale, and share across teams compared to individual ad-hoc commands.

