# Real-World Example

Let's combine everything.

Create:

```bash id="t10a053"
touch deploy-web.yml
```

Add:

```yaml id="t10a054"
---
- name: Deploy Web Application

  hosts: web

  become: true

  vars:

    app_user: webadmin

  tasks:

    - name: Install nginx

      dnf:
        name: nginx
        state: present

    - name: Create application user

      user:
        name: "{{ app_user }}"
        state: present

    - name: Create application directory

      file:
        path: /opt/webapp
        state: directory

    - name: Deploy homepage

      copy:
        content: "Welcome to Ansible Automation"
        dest: /usr/share/nginx/html/index.html

      notify:
        - Restart nginx

    - name: Start nginx

      service:
        name: nginx
        state: started
        enabled: true

  handlers:

    - name: Restart nginx

      service:
        name: nginx
        state: restarted
```

